{
  "stem": "8947.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this is-- I don't know it's doing to-- due to the stress, or they administered something.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because we-- I wasn't the only one, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We lost our periods.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it lasted.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It lasted for a year.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, now you are-- you are coming to a very, very terrible subject, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because you see, there were women who were pregnant.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But at the time that they entered, they-- it wasn't visible.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when it was visible-- I know we had a-- a pregnant woman among us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You tried to hide that person as much as you can.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then we-- it's known.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's known.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If she was discovered, she would go to the gas chambers, she and the-- so if a physician had access-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were-- we heard that in some camps a physician had access.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They would inject the mother so the baby dies, so they save the mother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And if a woman gave birth to the baby, they would kill-- they would inject the baby.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because otherwise, the mother would go toge-- I mean, there were some horrible things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was a horrible thing to be pregnant in Asuchwitz, horrible thing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But these things happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I know for sure, that-- that there were-- because we-- we heard these-- there were not only rumors that if a physician, you know, for somehow got access, you know, to work-- I don't know-- in-- in-- to-- to-- to work, and had access to medication, she would do it.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Bremen, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But Rudolf Ferdinand Hoss was in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember Kramer in Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We called him the beast of Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Bremen-- see, in Bremen, I can't remember any of the commandants.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, what they did-- they really hauled us out from Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
